<%# The Maysa Method™ — the philosophy page. NeuSkin Clinic (standalone) design port. English / LTR. %>

<%# ---- Hero (stacked: eyebrow → h2 → h1) ---- %>
<section class="page-hero mm-hero" data-controller="reveal">
  <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal="fade">The Philosophy</span>
  <h2 class="mm-hero-sub" data-reveal="mask" data-reveal-delay="160"><span>Skin is data.</span></h2>
  <h1 class="mm-hero-main" data-reveal="mask" data-reveal-delay="320"><span>Read it, then treat it.</span></h1>
</section>

<%# ---- The principle (2-col) ---- %>
<section class="section section--surface" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="section-inner split" style="align-items:start">
    <h2 data-reveal="up" style="font-size:clamp(1.6rem,2.6vw,2.4rem); color:var(--text-bright)">The principle</h2>
    <p class="lead" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="120">The Maysa Method™ is not a treatment. It is a way of deciding. Before anything is recommended, we read the skin, hair and body as a single connected system and let that reading — not a menu — decide what comes next.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- Four pillars ---- %>
<section class="section section--surface" data-controller="reveal" style="padding-top:0">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="cols cols-4" data-reveal="up">
      <div class="col"><span class="num">Pillar 01</span><h3>Skin</h3><p>Barrier, tone, texture and pigment — read, then restored in order.</p></div>
      <div class="col"><span class="num">Pillar 02</span><h3>Hair</h3><p>Scalp health and density, assessed clinically and supported over weeks.</p></div>
      <div class="col"><span class="num">Pillar 03</span><h3>Body</h3><p>Tone, contour and posture — measured, not guessed, and supported clinically.</p></div>
      <div class="col"><span class="num">Pillar 04</span><h3>Lifestyle</h3><p>Sleep, sun, stress and habit — the quiet inputs that decide how the rest holds.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- What it is not (LIGHT contrast band, 2-col) ---- %>
<section class="section section--light" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="section-inner split" style="align-items:start">
    <div data-reveal="up">
      <span class="eyebrow">What it is not</span>
      <h2 style="margin-top:22px; font-size:clamp(1.9rem,3.4vw,3rem)">Discipline is mostly <span class="em">restraint.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <ul class="exclude" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="120">
      <li>It is not a treatment, and nothing is performed during it.</li>
      <li>It is not a quick fix; good skin is sequenced over time.</li>
      <li>It is not a price list, and it is never sold from a menu.</li>
      <li>It is not for everyone — and that is entirely intentional.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- A year, in four movements — pinned horizontal scroller ---- %>
<section class="hscroll" data-controller="hscroll">
  <div class="hscroll-pin">
    <div class="hscroll-track" data-hscroll-target="track">
      <div class="hscroll-intro">
        <span class="eyebrow">The 12-month timeline</span>
        <h2>A year, in <span class="em">four movements.</span></h2>
        <p>The Maysa Method™ unfolds over four quarters — measured, reviewed, adjusted. Scroll through the year.</p>
        <div class="cue">Scroll →</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hpanel"><h4 class="q">Q1</h4><h3>Diagnose</h3><p>Baseline captured, the plan written. The slow, invisible work begins.</p></div>
      <div class="hpanel"><h4 class="q">Q2</h4><h3>Restore</h3><p>Targeted correction across the four pillars, reviewed against baseline.</p></div>
      <div class="hpanel"><h4 class="q">Q3</h4><h3>Build</h3><p>Results compounded; the plan adjusted to how your skin responded.</p></div>
      <div class="hpanel"><h4 class="q">Q4</h4><h3>Maintain</h3><p>A maintenance rhythm set, and a record you keep for the years ahead.</p></div>
      <div class="hshot-outro">
        <blockquote>“Skin is data. Read it across a year, and it stops surprising you.”</blockquote>
        <%= link_to "Request the Assessment", inquire_path(codeword: "METHOD"), class: "btn", style: "align-self:flex-start" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- Closing CTA ---- %>
<section class="cta-center" data-controller="reveal">
  <h2 class="reveal" data-reveal-target="item">Begin with the <span class="em">Maysa Method™.</span></h2>
  <p class="reveal d1" data-reveal-target="item">One reading, one written plan, reviewed every quarter. It begins with a private inquiry.</p>
  <p class="reveal d2" data-reveal-target="item"><%= link_to "Request the Assessment", inquire_path(codeword: "METHOD", persona: "unsure"), class: "btn" %></p>
</section>
